---
title: Turkish-Spiced Lamb Patties with Couscous
description: We're mad for lamb and these DIY lamb patties flavoured with Turkish spices and garlic don't disappoint. Fluffy pepita-spiked couscous and roasted veggies coated in a parsley vinaigrette combine for the perfect side!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/galettes-dagneau-a-la-turque-8fba3415.jpg
